Scholze\nconstruction explored recently by Hansen, to give a more precise description of\nthe cohomology of this local Shimura variety, verifying a strong form of the\nKottwitz conjecture in the process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Sep 2021 20:59:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2022 22:53:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-06"}
