le geometry is chosen, in which both assumed coordinate systems agree.\nMost notably, the $f(Q)$ class of theories falls into this class.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Sep 2021 17:10:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Dec 2021 19:01:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-03"}
